from the Elemental Planes that appears in an unoccupied space within range. Choose the spirit's element, which determines its damage type: air (Lightning), earth (Thunder), fire (Fire), or water (Cold). The spirit lasts for the duration.\n\nWhenever a creature you can see enters the spirit's space or starts its turn within 5 feet of the spirit, you can force that creature to make a Dexterity saving throw if the spirit has no creature Restrained. On failed save, the target takes 8d8 damage of the spirit's type, and the target has the Restrained condition until the spell ends. At the start of each of its turns, the Restrained target repeats the save. On a failed save, the target takes 4d8 damage of the spirit's type. On a successful save, the target isn't Restrained by the spirit"},"higher_level_description":{"value":"The damage increases by 2d8 for each spell slot level above 5"},"classes":{"value":["druid","wizard"]},"dice":{"value":[]},"updated_at":{"value":"2024-12-20T18:50:46.648943"},"id":"811e92de-9f6d-4ab9-90bd-40a038502021"}}},"updated_at":{"value":"2024-12-20T18:50:35.826315"},"id":"0d90ff21-30a6-4521-a411-c7398eda5e87"}},{"system":"5e2024","resource_id":"effect","stats":{"name":{"value":"Cast Tsunami (5 Charges)"},"trigger_type":{"value":"active"},"trigger_condition":{"value":{"system":"5e2024","resource_id":"trigger_condition_or","stats":{"id":"d9e3201d-1595-49b5-9c42-0a9720e37546"}}},"recharge_type":{"value":"formula"},"recharges":{"value":{"system":"5e2024","resource_id":"dice_roll","stats":{"id":"92567735-e310-442a-b31e-8524c92fca3e"}}},"type":{"value":"use_spell"},"spell":{"value":{"system":"5e2024","resource_id":"spell","stats":{"name":{"value":"Tsunami"},"source":{"value":"phb"},"level":{"value":"spell_level_8"},"school":{"value":"spell_school_conjuration"},"casting_time":{"value":"1 minute"},"range":{"value":"1 mile"},"duration":{"value":"Concentration, up to 6 rounds"},"verbal":{"value":true},"somatic":{"value":true},"description":{"value":"A wall of water springs into existence at a point you choose within range. You can make the wall up to 300 feet long, 300 feet high, and 50 feet thick. The wall lasts for the duration.\n\nWhen the wall appears, each creature in its area makes a Strength saving throw, taking 6d10 Bludgeoning damage on a failed save or half as much damage on a successful one.\n\nAt the start of each of your turns after the wall appears, the wall, along with any creatures in it, moves 50 feet away from you. Any Huge or smaller creature inside the wall or whose space the wall enters when it moves must succeed on a Strength saving throw or take 5d10 Bludgeoning damage. A creature can take this damage only once per round. At the end of the turn, the wall's height is reduced by 50 feet, and the damage the wall deals on later rounds is reduced by 1d10. When the wall reaches 0 feet in height, the spell ends.\n\nA creature caught in the wall can move by swimming. Because of the wave's force, though, the creature must succeed on a Strength (Athletics) check against your spell save DC to move at all. If it fails the check, it can't move. A creature that moves out of the wall falls to the ground"},"classes":{"value":["druid"]},"dice":{"value":[{"system":"5e2024","resource_id":"levelled_damage_dice","stats":{"level":{"value":8},"damage_dice":{"value":[{"system":"5e2024","resource_id":"damage_dice","stats":{"dices":{"value":[{"system":"5e2024","resource_id":"dice_roll","stats":{"dice_amount":{"value":6},"dice_type":{"value":"d10"},"updated_at":{"value":"2024-12-20T18:50:46.642594"},"id":"2ce07d18-53e0-49b7-83a8-9c03081c2f81"}}]},"damage_type":{"value":"bludgeoning"},"updated_at":{"value":"2024-12-20T18:50:46.642600"},"id":"f3615b9b-0974-408f-a32e-9814a0cb50f2"}}]},"updated_at":{"value":"2024-12-20T18:50:46.642606"},"id":"f0a9ca34-dee4-41ed-bc2b-7b548c7ee22d"}}]},"updated_at":{"value":"2024-12-20T18:50:46.642609"},"id":"cf32dd77-2982-4146-aedf-fc03c9c29bb6"}}},"updated_at":{"value":"2024-12-20T18:50:35.82